# System Requirement for HyprArch

## MINIMUM

CPU: **potato**   
GPU: Integrated    
MEMORY: ~2GB (i tested in a vm and it just used 800MB)   
STORAGE: 20GB   
INTERNET/ETHERNET: Yes   

## RECOMENDED

CPU: Somewhat Modern   
GPU: Low end or GPU ~8GB VRAM   
MEMORY: 8-16 GB    
STORAGE: 50-70 GB   
INTERNET/ETHERNET: Yes   

## MAXIMUM

Everything better than before
